                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Talbotton, Ga.</placeName>\n                                        <date>Sept. 27. 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p><addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser Esq.</addressee>!</p>\n                              <p>Dear Sir!</p>\n                              <p>We the undersigned chosen officer's of the hebrew<lb/> benevolent\n                                        society of <placeName>Talbotton Ga.</placeName> are\n                                        taking<lb/> the liberty to inform you of the following\n                                        resolutions <sic>wich</sic> have been <sic>past</sic> by a\n                                        majority<lb/> of the members of said society at their\n                                        last<lb/> meeting held at the <date>18</date> inst.\n                                        requesting you to<lb/> insert the same in the next Occident\n                                        for <sic>wich</sic> you<lb/> will please forward your\n                                        account for payment<lb/> to this place.</p>\n                              <p>Resolved, that all the money <sic>wich</sic> is in\n                                                  <sic>posession</sic> of<lb/> the hebrew benevolent\n                                        society of this place<lb/>\n                                        <sic>wich</sic> amounts to fifty Dollars shall be\n                                        apropi<lb/>ated to buy a <sic>silvre</sic> ornament for a\n                                        sefer Torah<lb/> in <sic>wich</sic> all the names of the\n                                        members shall be<lb/> engraved.</p>\n                              <p>Resolved, that the same shall be presented to the newly<lb/>\n                                        <sic>build</sic> congregation <del>of</del> in the of\n                                                  <placeName>Williamsburgh</placeName><lb/> state of\n                                                  <placeName>New-York</placeName>.</p>\n                              <p>Resolved, that <persName>Mr. Moses Selig</persName> is chosen to\n                                        present<lb/> the same after its completion to the\n                                        President<lb/> of said congregation in the month of\n                                                  <date><sic>february</sic></date><lb/> next.</p>\n                              <p>Resolved, that the forgoing resolutions shall be printed<lb/> in\n                                        the next Occident.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\"><persName>Morris Selz</persName>. Pres.</p>\n                              <p><persName role=\"author\">Abraham Cahn</persName>, Sec.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3zw19c6k/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
