                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>Following are the names of the members of the<lb/> society:</p>\n                              <list type=\"simple\">\n                                        <head/>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName>Morris Selz</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName>Moses Selig</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName>Gabriel Selig</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName>Samuel Straus</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName>Leopold Straus</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName>Meyer Kayser</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName role=\"author\">Abraham Kahn</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                                        <item>\n                                                  <persName>Solomon Meyer</persName>\n                                        </item>\n                              </list>\n                              <p>Should any thing be incorrect in this lines in the<lb/> way of\n                                        spelling or any other way we beg you<lb/> to correct if for\n                                        we are all inexperienced hands.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Respectfully</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\"><persName role=\"author\">Abr. Cahn</persName>\n                                        sec.</p>"
                  },
